WEBVTT

00:08:57.720 --> 00:09:00.943
we must step up and replace
elections with sortition.

00:09:01.332 --> 00:09:02.586
I have hope.

00:09:02.610 --> 00:09:04.942
Here in Hungary,
systems have been created,

00:09:04.966 --> 00:09:07.053
and systems have been
torn down and replaced

00:09:07.077 --> 00:09:08.286
in the past.

00:09:08.310 --> 00:09:11.126
Change can and does happen.

00:09:11.150 --> 00:09:13.762
It's just a matter of when and how.

00:09:13.786 --> 00:09:15.389
Thank you.
(Hungarian) Thank you.

00:09:15.413 --> 00:09:18.017
(Applause)